created: 20260502012000000
modified: 20260502012000000
type: text/markdown

- In TiddlyWiki, create a new tiddler
- Set Type to `text/css`
- Add the tag `$:/tags/Stylesheet`
- Paste the entire CSS into the tiddler body
- Save --- it applies instantly, no reload needed
